# MaxisLiquid

MaxisLiquid is a personal financial operations dashboard.  
It centralizes my trading activity, portfolio tracking, watchlists, and real-life expenses into a single system.

The goal is visibility and decision quality.  
I do not want information split across broker apps, exchange apps, spreadsheets, and notes.

This is not a trading bot and not an auto-trader.  
It is a control panel for my financial state.

---

## Purpose

Right now financial data lives in separate places:
- brokerage accounts
- crypto exchanges
- banking apps
- manual spreadsheets
- screenshots
- memory

Because of this, I cannot reliably answer simple questions:
- my real net worth
- risk exposure
- position sizing
- how much I actually spend
- whether I am outperforming or underperforming

MaxisLiquid exists to remove uncertainty.

Primary objective:
Create a single source of truth for my money.

---

